Query 2: Toggle (1 1 3): Toggle synapses on path 1-3.


Path 1-3: 1-2-3 (edges: 1-2, 2-3).

If edges 1-2, 2-3 are inactive, then toggle to active.

Active edges: 1-2, 2-3.


Query 3: Query (2 1 3): Count active synapses on path 1-3.


Path 1-3: 1-2-3 (edges: 1-2, 2-3).

Active edges on path: 1-2, 2-3 (2 edges).

Total active: 2.

